{"tid":571421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴管理層願對話　車長組織暫停工業行動","createTime":"2018-02-24T15:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T16:18:04.000Z","uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dfd77f22f7c84e175af1b3942723f75d348e2532","tid":571421,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:46:28.000Z","msg":"九巴管理層願對話　車長組織暫停工業行動<br />\n2018-02-24 HKT 23:21<br />\n<br />\n九巴車長組織「月薪車長大聯盟」晚上發起工業行動，發起人葉蔚琳表示，由於九巴管理層即將到尖東麼地道總站和車長對話，她感到高興，會暫停工業行動，亦不會到禮賓府靜坐，暫時不會有下一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n在尖東麼地道巴士總站，有市民到場聲援九巴車長，有人舉起寫上「加油」的紙張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1382405-20180224.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1382405-20180224.htm&d=HfNrgXPymsOIlUf6%2B%2FTneMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=59c3e122\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1382405-20180224.htm&h=76f49d6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1382405-20180224.htm</a>"},{"pid":"137b89e0704be48c22fca5a7d819e9017c942195","tid":571421,"uid":73915,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:48:14.000Z","msg":"又對話<br />\n雨革林鄭同學生對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a890580ae695f0f769b3b9e591722eb31a3d8984","tid":571421,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1382405_1_20180224232311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1382405_1_20180224232311.jpg&h=20e5f555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葉蔚琳表示，會暫停工業行動，亦不會到禮賓府靜坐。（港台圖片）<br />\n2018-02-24 HKT 23:23"},{"pid":"6a9346bd0acfda7b814d100a2ba901e8112dd0f3","tid":